OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FChildren under the age of five should
OL,8,Fnot be on screens for more than an
OL,9,Fhour a day, parents will be told in
OL,10,Fnew advice issued by the government.
OL,12,FThe advice also says that screen time
OL,13,Ffor children under two should be
OL,14,Favoided, other than for shared
OL,15,Factivities encouraging interaction.
OL,17,FIssuing the new advice, the prime
OL,18,Fminister vowed that parents will not
OL,19,Fbe left to battle screens alone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
