PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer promised the new
OL,8,Fguidance would help families to keep
OL,9,Fchildren safe and make sure they build
OL,10,Fhealthy habits with screens.
OL,12,F"Parenting in a digital world can feel
OL,13,Frelentless," he said, "screens are
OL,14,Feverywhere, and the advice is often
OL,15,Fconflicting.
OL,17,F"My government will not leave parents
OL,18,Fto face this battle alone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
