PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShared screen time activities which
OL,8,Finclude talking and asking questions
OL,9,Fabout the content is also better for a
OL,10,Fchild's cognitive development than
OL,11,Fletting them use screens alone, the
OL,12,Fguidance will say.
OL,14,FThose shared activities include video
OL,15,Fcalling friends or family, or looking
OL,16,Fthrough photos together.
OL,18,FThe prime minister said he understood
OL,19,Fthere may be opposition to the advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
