PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSir Keir said: "There will be some who
OL,8,Fwill oppose us doing this.
OL,10,F"But whether it's navigating
OL,11,Ftechnology, tackling the cost of
OL,12,Fliving or balancing the demands of
OL,13,Ffamily life, I will always stand on
OL,14,Fthe side of parents doing their best
OL,15,Ffor their children."
OL,17,FAround 98% of children are watching
OL,18,Fscreens on a daily basis by the age of
OL,19,Ftwo, the government had previously
OL,20,Fsaid, with high screen time seeing an
OL,21,Fimpact on children's language.
