PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FLong periods of time spent on screens
OL,8,Falone impacts activities key for good
OL,9,Fdevelopment such as sleep, physical
OL,10,Factivity, creative play and
OL,11,Finteraction with parents, the panel
OL,12,Ffound in its review of the evidence.
OL,14,FThe new guidance developed by a panel
OL,15,Fled by children's commissioner Dame
OL,16,FRachel de Souza and children's health
OL,17,Fexpert Professor Russell Viner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
