PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774828709
OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe panel warned, however, that the
OL,8,Flimits on screen time should not be
OL,9,Fapplied in the same way for children
OL,10,Fwith special educational needs and
OL,11,Fdisabilities, who may need to use
OL,12,Fscreen-based assistive technologies.
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,15,Fsaid: "I know how hard it is to
OL,16,Fnavigate parenting in a world full of
OL,17,Fscreens.
OL,19,F"They're unavoidable, but it often
OL,20,Ffeels impossible to tell whether
OL,21,Fyou're getting the balance right.
