OL,3,CScreen time for under-fives should be
OL,4,Climited to an hour a day, government
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"That's why we're giving parents the
OL,8,Fclear, trusted support they've asked
OL,9,Ffor ` so families can make informed
OL,10,Fchoices, and children can have the
OL,11,Fchildhood they deserve."
